    "description": "A Whisper in the Twilight is a first person Mystery/Sci-Fi/Puzzle game. A wholly unique player experience, aiming to reinvent the single-player genre.<br><br>The game will be released in ten self-contained Chapters.<br>&quot;CHAPTER TWO: THE CRYING MOUNTAINS&quot; is the second one.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039340/extras/a992db40b86453519d3ccd66bdbab0ce.avif?t=1721323120\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br>In this second chapter of the saga, new challenges, and characters both familiar and unknown, will draw you into an intense narrative adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039340/extras/406634ff3da53e9872e55498edf40e86.avif?t=1721323120\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br>The journey towards the dark city of Zhar is long, but bide your time and immerse yourself fully. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039340/extras/6188ddce17a577fe91d4879251978dc3.avif?t=1721323120\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br>You will find that saving your sister is not your only task: the shape of your destiny will shift as mysterious entities offer revelation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039340/extras/0f5540c8dd15960de6b6606257dc1d4c.avif?t=1721323120\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br>And through travel and travail we will unlock the way forward.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039340/extras/e0afcfb5cde69a5605040c6c68b0a5de.avif?t=1721323120\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br>May the Seven Spirits of the Stones be with you. Qadambar!",
